import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='disease', data=data, label='Disease Cases')
    plt.title('What is the trend of disease cases over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Disease Cases')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    data['month'] = data['date'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')
    monthly_avg = data.groupby('month')['disease'].mean().reset_index()

    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax = sns.barplot(x='month', y='disease', data=monthly_avg)
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45)
    plt.axhline(monthly_avg['disease'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Average: {monthly_avg['disease'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the average number of disease cases per month?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['total'] = data['wounds'] + data['other'] + data['disease']
    data['wounds_percentage'] = data['wounds'] / data['total']
    data['other_percentage'] = data['other'] / data['total']
    data['disease_percentage'] = data['disease'] / data['total']

    disease_types = ['Wounds', 'Other', 'Disease']
    disease_percentages = [data['wounds_percentage'].mean(), data['other_percentage'].mean(), data['disease_percentage'].mean()]

    plt.pie(disease_percentages, labels=disease_types, autopct='%1.1f%%')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of disease cases by type of disease?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(disease_types, loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
